snippet.textDisplay: For real, this is low-key horror when you think about it. You're trapped for at least the rest of your life in a shitty club, with blaring techno/dance music, sugary party drinks, and maybe some bar snacks, where everyone else just dances mindlessly without responding to you or your cries for help. It might even last LONGER than just the rest of your life, because they kill themselves and just walk back into the party. There's virtually no escape...it's kinda terrifying.
